flashcards
groups/decks
select and train multiple groups/decks
select and train by (class or) category
cards appear more often the lower your success-rate is
cards that havent appeared for a while will always appear 

card struct {
    word in lang1 / question
    word in lang2 / answer
    (class)
    categories
    has appeared n times
    sucessful n times
    last appeared
}

(class enum {
    phrase
    verb
    noun
    adjective
    other
})

load into memory at start of training
offload to db after training

db-api:

GET /Decks []string
GET /Decks/<name> Deck
PUT /Decks/<name>